  fishType: Salmon
  displayName: Salmon
  difficulty: 1
  educationalInfo: Salmon has a distinctive spine and numerous pin bones that need
    careful removal. The pin bones run along the lateral line and must be pulled
    out gently with tweezers to avoid breaking them.
  description: Popular fish known for its rich flavor and omega-3 content. Moderate
    bone complexity.
  timeLimitSeconds: 180
  spineBoneCount: 3
  ribBoneCount: 10
  pinBoneCount: 1
  habitat: Both freshwater and saltwater environments
  cookingTips: Salmon is best grilled or baked. Remove all pin bones before cooking
    for the best experience. The rich oil content makes it very flavorful.
